caption:
#Repost @davidofdaveart of new @hank30nyr #NYR mask! Description below.  
The next chapter of Henrik Lundqvist's mask art is here.  To paint and create has been my dream job for 20 years. I am so thankful to paint for awesome goalies all over the world.  I will always work hard for you.  The Rangers Razors are unleashed in a totally wild way on this mask. They creates a bold design with insane Rangers contrasts . I love to always try to think outside the box and always move forward with new ideas every day . It all creates a mask that is 100% New York, 100% Rangers, 100% Lundqvist.  Henrik and I have worked together for soon two decades, we brainstorm a lot and it is always so creative and fun to play with the colors with you Henrik 
@hank30nyr @nyrangers @nhl #daveart #daveartthecradleofcreativity #nhl @bauergoalie

